OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FThomas Tuchel still has "no regrets"
OL,7,Fabout his decisions in England's
OL,8,Fpainful World Cup semi-final loss to
OL,9,FArgentina and claimed fan opinions
OL,10,Fwill not impact how he views his
OL,11,Ffuture.
OL,13,FThe nation had been dreaming of a
OL,14,Ffirst men's World Cup final since
OL,15,Flifting the trophy since 1966 but are
OL,16,Fnow in the midst of an uncomfortable
OL,17,Fexamination of shortcomings.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
