OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FSir Gareth Southgate's successor was
OL,7,Fbrought in to turn nearly men into
OL,8,Ftrophy winners, but England stumbled
OL,9,Fafter taking a 55th-minute lead on
OL,10,FWednesday and Argentina capitalised in
OL,11,Fa chaotic late 2-1 turnaround.
OL,13,FThe statistics are as bleak as the
OL,14,Fsecond half was to watch, but Tuchel
OL,15,Fstuck to his guns ahead of Saturday's
OL,16,Funwanted bronze medal match against
OL,17,FFrance, having had 48 hours to stew on
OL,18,Fthe defeat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"I view them in the same way," the
OL,7,FEngland boss said when asked if his
OL,8,Fview on the performance had changed.
OL,9,F"I view them in the same way that we
OL,10,Fwere too passive, we got too passive.
OL,12,F"If you are asking if I regret my
OL,13,Fdecision, if this is the question
OL,14,Fthen, no, I don't regret my decisions
OL,15,Fbecause I felt that we'd become too
OL,16,Fpassive.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@^O]qD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"I felt that the momentum switches in
OL,7,Fthe match and I tried to help my team.
OL,8,FI tried to help, I tried to support.
OL,10,F"I took several decisions trusting my
OL,11,Finstinct, my intuition, my experience,
OL,12,Ftrusting my competitiveness, and I
OL,13,Ftook the decision in order to help the
OL,14,Fteam and get the result.
OL,16,F"We didn't get the result, so I take,
OL,17,Fof course, the responsibility for
OL,18,Fthese decisions but the decisions are
OL,19,Fmade under stress, the decisions are
OL,20,Fmade in-game. This is in-game life,
OL,21,Flive coaching.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"I would regret if I didn't help. I
OL,7,Fwould regret if we didn't react. But I
OL,8,Fhave no regrets over the decision
OL,9,Fitself."
OL,11,FThat answer started with him giving
OL,12,Fshort shrift to United States
OL,13,FPresident Donald Trump's criticism `
OL,14,F"do you use Donald Trump as your
OL,15,Fwitness for the case or...?" ` and set
OL,16,Fthe tone for a tense press conference.
OL,18,FTrump had chimed in with criticism
OL,19,Fover Tuchel's approach against
OL,20,FArgentina, saying that his use of
OL,21,FHarry Kane was "unusual".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]vD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"You have a great player in England,
OL,7,Fwho I played golf with," Trump said in
OL,8,Fa press conference. "You know that,
OL,9,Fright? He is Harry, who's been
OL,10,Ffantastic.
OL,12,F"I think they perhaps made a mistake
OL,13,Fwhen they made him a defensive player.
OL,14,FWhat do I know about soccer? They took
OL,15,Fthe lead, and they took their best
OL,16,Fplayer and put him on defence," Trump
OL,17,Fsaid in a press conference with Fifa
OL,18,FPresident Gianni Infantino.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XO]pD@UOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
