PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FTuchel also spoke of the "scar" they
OL,7,Fall now "have to live with" and
OL,8,Frefused to engage in the "blame game"
OL,9,Fas outsiders question the Football
OL,10,FAssociation's decision to hand him a
OL,11,Ftwo-year contract extension ahead of
OL,12,Fthe World Cup.
OL,14,FThe England boss retains the governing
OL,15,Fbody's backing and stressed after the
OL,16,FArgentina match that he was "100 per
OL,17,Fcent" committed to leading the side
OL,18,Finto the home Euros in 2028.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUnD@_O]oD@IOUoD@[O]pD@ZOUpD@eO]xD@
OL,26,A]OUyD@EO]
