PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FAsked if a change in fan sentiment
OL,7,Fcould alter his stance, Tuchel said he
OL,8,Fwould "like to make (his own) picture".
OL,10,F"I think it is a strong statement that
OL,11,Fyou give here and be the advocate for
OL,12,Fhalf of the country being against me
OL,13,Fand a split country. Let's wait for
OL,14,Fthat. I have nothing more... what is
OL,15,Fthe question?"
OL,26,@pD@UpmpD@]pnrD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FWhen the reporter asked whether more
OL,7,Ffans deciding he should go would
OL,8,Fchange his thoughts about staying on,
OL,9,Fhe retorted: "No, it can never change
OL,10,Fmy thinking if I would like to carry
OL,11,Fon."
OL,13,FThat is a sea change in approach to
OL,14,Fpredecessor Southgate, who walked away
OL,15,Fafter the Euro 2024 final defeat to
OL,16,FSpain having repeatedly said he did
OL,17,Fnot want to outstay his welcome.
OL,26,@qD@NOUsD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,FBut Tuchel is ready to plough on
OL,7,Fundeterred as he looks to close the
OL,8,Fgap on Sunday's World Cup finalists
OL,9,Fand third-placed play-off opponents
OL,10,FFrance.
OL,12,F"I think the gap is there because of
OL,13,Fthe titles that Argentina, France and
OL,14,FSpain have has national teams, as
OL,15,Fcountries, what they built over many
OL,16,Fyears with the coaches and the team,"
OL,17,Fthe England boss said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784431087
OL,3,CThomas Tuchel has 'no regrets' over
OL,4,CEngland tactics in World Cup semi-final
OL,6,F"There is still a slight gap that we
OL,7,Fhave to close. The gap shows in almost
OL,8,Fthe expectations of these countries to
OL,9,Fwin the World Cup and be in the final.
OL,11,F"I think we demanded it from ourselves
OL,12,Fwithin camp, for sure. We dreamed
OL,13,Fabout it, we pushed for it and we
OL,14,Fcompeted for it but there is still a
OL,15,Fgap to close in the way how to play
OL,16,Ffootball under pressure and the way to
OL,17,Fimplement yourself on the very next
OL,18,Flevel."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
